<template>
  <ion-page>
    <ion-header>
      <ion-toolbar>
        <ion-title>SettingsFragment</ion-title>
      </ion-toolbar>
    </ion-header>
    <ion-content :fullscreen="true">
      <ion-header collapse="condense">
        <ion-toolbar>
          <ion-title size="large">SettingsFragment</ion-title>
        </ion-toolbar>
      </ion-header>

      <ExploreContainer name="SettingsFragment page" />

      <ion-list>
        <ion-item>
          <ion-label>Idioma</ion-label>
          <ion-select :selectOptions="g" value="idioma" interface="action-sheet" ok-text="Aceptar" cancel-text="Cancelar"  placeholder="Select One">
            <ion-select-option value="es">Español</ion-select-option>
            <ion-select-option value="ca">Català</ion-select-option>
            <ion-select-option value="en">English</ion-select-option>
          </ion-select>
        </ion-item>
      </ion-list>
    </ion-content>
  </ion-page>
</template>

<script>
import {
  IonPage,
  IonHeader,
  IonToolbar,
  IonTitle,
  IonContent,
  IonList,
  IonItem,
  IonLabel,
  IonSelect,
  IonSelectOption,
} from "@ionic/vue";
import ExploreContainer from "../components/ExploreContainer.vue";

export default {
  name: "SettingsFragment",
  components: {
    ExploreContainer,
    IonHeader,
    IonToolbar,
    IonTitle,
    IonContent,
    IonPage,
    IonList,
    IonItem,
    IonLabel,
    IonSelect,
    IonSelectOption,
  },
  data: function () {
    return {
      g:{
        cssClass: 'remove-cancel'
      }
    };
  },
  methods: {},
};
</script>

<style lang="css">
.remove-cancel {
    .alert-button:nth-child(1) {
        display: none;
    }
}
</style>
